reviewText: Lo tomé porque me obligaron

I​ had to pay in order to know my marks in the tests and in order to get the course finished. I didn't like that, since I hadn't had to do it in the previous courses and I didn't expect I would have to do it in this one. The course is great, as everything to do with Barbara Oakley, it is just that I felt forced to pay if I wanted to get the course finished and the marks on the tests; as I mentioned before, I didn't expect it (it didn't happen before) and I didn't like it at all.
Cuando terminé la primera semana me quiere obligar a pagar el certificado para poder dejarme terminar el curso. Pero no quiero el certificado, quería concluir el curso. Por esa razón me daré de baja
